name: Skype for Business Diagnostics
description: Creates files with information about Skype calls and calculates metrics of the last 24h.

inputs.description: Minimum number of seconds to consider a call as a short call
inputs.name: MinSecondsForCall

inputs.description: Number of hours to consider an unfinished call as a dropped call
inputs.name: NumHoursForTimeout

outputs.description: Total number of calls (audio + video + screen sharing)
outputs.name: TotalCalls

outputs.description: Total number of audio calls
outputs.name: TotalAudio

outputs.description: Percentage of poor quality audio calls
outputs.name: PoorAudioPerc

outputs.description: Percentage of poor quality audio calls over Ethernet
